#############
Release Notes
#############

0.6
---
* Released: 2020-03-30
* Added :obj:`~flutils.txtutils.len_without_ansi`
* Added :obj:`~flutils.txtutils.AnsiTextWrapper`
* Added :obj:`~flutils.cmdutils.run`


0.5
---

* Released: 2020-02-20
* Added :obj:`~flutils.namedtupleutils.to_namedtuple`
* Works with `Python3.8 <https://www.python.org/downloads/>`_

0.4
---

* Released: 2019-07-16
* Added :obj:`~flutils.setuputils.add_setup_cfg_commands`
* Added :obj:`~flutils.strutils.as_escaped_unicode_literal`
* Added :obj:`~flutils.strutils.as_escaped_utf8_literal`
* Added :obj:`~flutils.strutils.convert_escaped_unicode_literal`
* Added :obj:`~flutils.strutils.convert_escaped_utf8_literal`
* Added the :ref:`b64` codecs via :obj:`~flutils.codecs.register_codecs`
* Added the :ref:`raw_utf8_escape` codec via :obj:`~flutils.codecs.register_codecs`
* Removed the restriction of Python string method names as identifiers in:

  * :obj:`~flutils.validators.validate_identifier`
  * :obj:`~flutils.moduleutils.cherry_pick`

* Rewrite of :obj:`~flutils.packages.bump_version`
* Improved unit and integration tests.

0.3
---

* Released: 2018-10-29
* Added :obj:`~flutils.packages.bump_version`

0.2
---

* Released: 2018-10-27
* Added :obj:`~flutils.decorators.cached_property`
* Works with `Python3.7 <https://www.python.org/downloads/>`_


0.1
---

* Released: 2018-07-06
* Initial release
* Works with `Python3.6 <https://www.python.org/downloads/>`_


